<article class="config-card config-card-soft">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">Tratamento</p>
      <h3>Configuracoes de limpeza</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="config-module-intro">
    <strong>Regras para analise e reprocesso</strong>
    <p>Escolha fila alvo, limite, modo e politica de reset. As acoes da pagina de uso vao respeitar esses parametros.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="form-grid maintenance-form">
    <label>
      <span>Fila alvo</span>
      <select id="maintenanceStrategy">
        <option value="short-multipage" selected>Texto curto em PDF grande</option>
        <option value="force-ocr">Forcar OCR novamente</option>
        <option value="recent-errors">Falhas recentes</option>
        <option value="short-indexed">Indexados com texto curto</option>
        <option value="null-method">Indexados sem metodo</option>
        <option value="empty-indexed">Indexados vazios</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Quantidade</span>
      <select id="maintenanceLimit">
        <option value="10" selected>10</option>
        <option value="25">25</option>
        <option value="50">50</option>
        <option value="100">100</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Modo de reprocesso</span>
      <select id="maintenanceMode">
        <option value="ocr" selected>OCR forcado</option>
        <option value="hybrid">Hibrido</option>
        <option value="native">Texto nativo</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line maintenance-toggle">
      <input id="maintenanceResetAttempts" type="checkbox" checked />
      <span>Zerar tentativas ao limpar</span>
    </label>
  </div>

  <div class="form-grid maintenance-form">
    <label>
      <span>Perfil de texto</span>
      <select id="textCleanupStrategy">
        <option value="low-quality" selected>Baixa legibilidade</option>
        <option value="payroll-layout">Folha e contracheque</option>
        <option value="long-lines">Linhas muito densas</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Quantidade</span>
      <select id="textCleanupLimit">
        <option value="5">5</option>
        <option value="10" selected>10</option>
        <option value="25">25</option>
        <option value="50">50</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Amostra de analise</span>
      <select id="textCleanupSampleSize">
        <option value="100">100</option>
        <option value="200" selected>200</option>
        <option value="500">500</option>
        <option value="1000">1000</option>
      </select>
    </label>
  </div>

  <p class="config-note">Use a pagina de operacao para rodar preview, limpeza ou reprocesso imediato usando estes parametros.</p>
</article>
